    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i read online that st johns wort is just a natural herb and usually pretty mild. my doctor didnt mention anything about it when he prescribed the sertraline, so i figured it would be fine to just supplement a bit. it's not like a heavy drug, right? i really just need that extra push for studying.",
