      "content": "i get what youre saying about the serotonin thing but i've actually taken some of these herbal capsules before without any problems. i feel like i'm just being extra paranoid because of the stress. like, if i just take a small dose, maybe like half a pill, wouldn't that basically negate the risk? surely a tiny bit won't make a huge difference compared to the sertraline i'm already on.",
