    "summary": "The user asks about combining Sertraline (an SSRI) with St. John's Wort to manage stress during finals. The assistant repeatedly and correctly warns the user about the risk of serotonin syndrome, emphasizes the dangers of mixing these substances regardless of dosage, and consistently directs the user to consult a medical professional.",
